    noria:networkInterfaceConnects noria:NetworkInterface008, noria:NetworkInterface002 .

# Ensure all entities are connected.
# All Resources are linked to Agents, ProductModels, Locations, and Applications.
# All NetworkInterfaces are linked to Resources and NetworkLinks.
# All NetworkLinks are linked to Resources and NetworkInterfaces.
# All Applications are linked to Agents and have modules.
# All ApplicationModules are linked to Applications, Agents/Orgs, and Resources.
# All Services are linked to Applications/Modules/Resources.
# All EventRecords are linked to ManagedObjects, ManagementSystems, and potentially Agents.
# All TroubleTickets are linked to Services/Applications/Resources, Agents, and EventRecords.
# All TroubleTicketNotes are linked to TroubleTickets and Agents.
# All ChangeRequests are linked to Services/Applications/Resources, Agents, and OperationPlans.
# All OperationPlans are linked to Pre/Post Conditions and can be referenced by ChangeRequests/EventRecords.
# All AnomalyPatterns are referenced by OperationPlans.
# All DocumentAttachments are linked to TroubleTickets/ChangeRequests.
# All Locations are linked to Sites and Resources.

# This graph is dense and connected, covering various aspects of the NORIA ontology.
